text: haey a l laoh chea anak del banhchoun khyal ruoch trong thveu aoy popk rsat . haey yeung ban sraochasrap vea( tukaphlieng) towleu srok tesa del slab( dei kmean chicheate) banteabmk yeung ban thveu aoy dei noh rsa laengvinh( meanchicheate) tamory vea kraoypi vea slab . kar thveu aoy rsa laengvinh( chenhpi phnaur) ka dauchnaoh der
